        {
            "title": "英超│曼聯聯賽18負+連續8輪不勝 熱刺今季輸25場 歐霸決賽交手前鬥衰",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"歐霸決賽交手前，曼聯、熱刺衰鬥衰。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c337f78da0c655e014ba64084455515d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250517/_2025051714211110899.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">歐霸決賽交手前，曼聯、熱刺衰鬥衰。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>下周三將在歐霸決賽交手的曼聯和熱刺，周五英超分途出擊同告敗陣，後者作客0:2不敵阿士東維拉，紅魔造訪車路士亦以0:1見負。兩隊今季完全衰鬥衰，曼聯連同今仗在本季聯賽已18負，目前又連續8輪不勝刷新多年恥辱性紀錄；而熱刺本季各有比賽已錄得25場敗仗，平了隊史最差紀錄，彼此都希望靠歐霸捧盃來遮醜。\n\n</p><h2>51年來首次聯賽單季輸18場</h2>\n<p>曼聯造訪車路士意外地強陣出擊，中堅哈利馬古尼、防守中場卡斯米路、隊長般奴費南迪斯全部正選，可是仍然未能搶分而回，被藍獅左閘古古列拿於71分鐘頭槌破網，最終輸0:1。連同今仗，紅魔目前於英超已8輪不勝，是隊史英超年代首次，亦是近35年來聯賽最差走勢。同時他們自1973至74球季後，首次於單季聯賽輸了18場，認賽失禮。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯51年來首次聯賽單季輸18場。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d77110d7491c4e2b36f372db3b45d64/2025-05/20_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯51年來首次聯賽單季輸18場。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯已連續8輪不勝，是英超年代首次。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b1df01b5d54858743aacaf43f25d57a/2025-05/21_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯已連續8輪不勝，是英超年代首次。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古古列拿取得個人今季英超第5個入球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/280cf8ac9f9ef0794d69a9d5a2de8ce7/2025-05/16_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古古列拿取得個人今季英超第5個入球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古古列拿為車路士開紀錄。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b9cb5844246e608024c44fe2d8f20871/2025-05/15_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古古列拿為車路士開紀錄。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"古古列拿為車路士頭槌建功。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ec5050081c29d058229ee5329038faa/2025-05/13_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古古列拿為車路士頭槌建功。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--nam