e\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿亦保持正選位置。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"海倫、美臣蒙特都正選出場。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8cfabcfd5fbdea98a16c9c09eeb0c33/2025-05/8_17.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海倫、美臣蒙特都正選出場。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"勞基梳爾同樣正選上陣。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/146ffd07f2119334c93c04b0dab6bff4/2025-05/7_27.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        勞基梳爾同樣正選上陣。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"正選出場的B費領黃牌。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/62f4ca26f5bcfe7ccf791d96cf02d456/2025-05/6_0_13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        正選出場的B費領黃牌。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般奴費南迪斯今場正選上陣。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/145b3817e8c0ab461f9a87c03c1068ce/2025-05/5_36.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般奴費南迪斯今場正選上陣。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"入球因為越位被推翻。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4847afab78653ca7316fe44b9b857199/2025-05/4_39.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        入球因為越位被推翻。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"哈利馬古尼無功而還。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/93ccd3110922990312421d94df0601a0/2025-05/3_45.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        哈利馬古尼無功而還。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"哈利馬古尼上半場曾經破門，可是越位在先被VAR推翻。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b777dedbcd87cd10b5b274a59a572abc/2025-05/1_47.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        哈利馬古尼上半場曾經破門，可是越位在先被VAR推翻。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>艾摩廉麾下英超均均0.92分</h2>\n<p>自去年11月執教曼聯以來，26次領軍出戰英超只得24分，場均0.92分的領隊魯賓艾摩廉直言歐霸決賽贏波就會完全不同：「今天我們運氣有點不好。有時我們想施加壓力並入球，但就注意力不集中，未能做到。5日後我們有歐霸決賽，球隊一定會悉力已赴，並為該仗準備好，如果到時贏了，情況就會完全不同。」\n\n</p><h2>熱刺今季輸25場平隊史紀錄</h2>\n<p>而熱刺盡派副選下，被維拉守將安斯干沙和中場保巴卡卡馬拉各入一球輸0:2，收錄本季各賽事第25場敗仗，追平隊史於1991至92球季創下的單季輸波場數最多的紀錄，與歐霸決賽對手曼聯一樣鬥衰。該隊領隊普斯迪高古亦矢言將一切押在歐霸決賽上：「下周三的比賽對球隊太重要了，那是決賽球季今季成敗的一場賽事。球員們在今場非常努力，沒有給對手太多機會，只是在對方破門後，信心有點動搖。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"熱刺今季各賽事已輸25場，平隊史最差紀錄。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0d33ab6f03e506a449c9b74691237d93/2025-05/20_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        熱刺今季各賽事已輸25場，平隊史最差紀錄。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"今季熱刺踢了58場，輸25場，落敗率達到43%。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1449467b4a3242c97381c66c9a88f244/2025-05/21_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        今季熱刺踢了58場，輸25場，落敗率達到43%。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保巴卡卡馬拉射入2:0。路透社\" class=\